      <abstract id="aspace_6f7f634efca99385bddda0f8b401139f">Founded in 1864, the J. Walter Thompson
        Company (JWT) is one of the oldest and largest enduring advertising agencies in the United
        States. Donald Armstrong was an advertising executive with J. Walter Thompson Company (JWT),
        Young &amp; Rubicam, and McCann-Erickson/Interpublic agencies.</abstract>
      <langmaterial id="aspace_f148fbcd946731369a53b234b9bced58">Materials in English</langmaterial>
    </did>
