    </arrangement>
    <bioghist id="aspace_2e99f7e4e89e594c197e2ff0ff5e0a7a">
      <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
      <p>Harvard class of 1937; Lehn &amp; Fink 1937-1939; Young &amp; Rubicam 1937-1945;
        McCann-Erickson (Interpublic)1946-1963; joined JWT 1963; Co-Director of JWT Review Board
        1966; Executive Vice President, JWT 1971; retired 1977. Died 1990.</p>
    </bioghist>
