      <head>Related Materials</head>
      <p>Related materials may be found in the following J. Walter Thompson Company Archives
        collections held in the Hartman Center:</p>
      <p>Account Files; Detroit Office. Goldfarb Consultants Ford Research Reports; International
        Offices; New Business Records; New York Office Records; Wallace Elton Papers.</p>
    </relatedmaterial>
    <scopecontent id="aspace_5fae6d1d67534c29cecd82076e5154a1">
      <head>Collection Overview</head>
      <p>Collection spans 1966-1972 and includes correspondence, research reports and other printed
        matter. Companies represented include Ford and Congoleum. Report topics include Puerto Rico,
        South Africa and the JWT Chicago Office. Acquired as part of the John W. Hartman Center for
        Sales, Advertising &amp; Marketing History.</p>
    </scopecontent>
